---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { siteConfig } from '../config';
---
<BaseLayout title={siteConfig.name} description={siteConfig.description}>
  <article>
    <section
      class="relative min-h-[70vh] flex items-center justify-center bg-cover bg-center pt-20 pb-24 md:pt-28 md:pb-32"
      style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1492725764893-90b379c2b6e7?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1920&q=80');"
      aria-labelledby="hero-title"
    >
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[var(--color-text)]/50" aria-hidden="true" />
      <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium tracking-wide text-white/90 uppercase mb-4">Bem-vinda</p>
        <h1 id="hero-title" class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-semibold text-white leading-tight mb-5 max-w-3xl mx-auto drop-shadow-sm">
          Maternidade Real e com Leveza
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/90 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed drop-shadow-sm">
          Um espaço para rotina, alimentação e saúde com simplicidade e afeto.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center min-h-[48px] px-8 py-3 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)] text-white font-medium hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity shadow-md">
            Ver artigos
          </a>
          <a href="/sobre" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center min-h-[48px] px-8 py-3 rounded-full border-2 border-white text-white font-medium hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
            Quem somos
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 -mt-6 pb-14">

    <section class="mb-16" aria-labelledby="categorias-title">
      <h2 id="categorias-title" class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-6 text-center">O que você encontra aqui</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <a href="/blog" class="block p-6 rounded-lg border border-[var(--color-border)] hover:border-[var(--color-accent)] hover:bg-white transition-colors">
          <div class="aspect-square rounded-md bg-[var(--color-rosa)] mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-[var(--color-accent)] text-3xl">☀️</div>
          <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-accent)]">Rotina</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-1">Organização do dia a dia com os pequenos.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/blog" class="block p-6 rounded-lg border border-[var(--color-border)] hover:border-[var(--color-accent)] hover:bg-white transition-colors">
          <div class="aspect-square rounded-md bg-[var(--color-rosa)] mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-[var(--color-accent)] text-3xl">🥗</div>
          <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-accent)]">Alimentação</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-1">Receitas e dicas para a família.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/blog" class="block p-6 rounded-lg border border-[var(--color-border)] hover:border-[var(--color-accent)] hover:bg-white transition-colors">
          <div class="aspect-square rounded-md bg-[var(--color-rosa)] mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-[var(--color-accent)] text-3xl">💚</div>
          <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-accent)]">Saúde</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-1">Cuidados e bem-estar para mães e filhos.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-16" aria-labelledby="posts-title">
      <h2 id="posts-title" class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-6">Últimos artigos</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <a href="/rotina-que-funciona" class="group block rounded-lg border border-[var(--color-border)] overflow-hidden hover:border-[var(--color-accent)] transition-colors">
          <div class="aspect-[4/3] bg-[var(--color-rosa)] flex items-center justify-center text-[var(--color-muted)] text-sm">Img</div>
          <div class="p-4">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] group-hover:text-[var(--color-accent)]">Rotina que funciona</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-1">Como organizar o dia com crianças.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/alimentacao-saudavel" class="group block rounded-lg border border-[var(--color-border)] overflow-hidden hover:border-[var(--color-accent)] transition-colors">
          <div class="aspect-[4/3] bg-[var(--color-rosa)] flex items-center justify-center text-[var(--color-muted)] text-sm">Img</div>
          <div class="p-4">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] group-hover:text-[var(--color-accent)]">Alimentação saudável</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-1">Ideias práticas para as refeições.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/cuidados-pos-parto" class="group block rounded-lg border border-[var(--color-border)] overflow-hidden hover:border-[var(--color-accent)] transition-colors">
          <div class="aspect-[4/3] bg-[var(--color-rosa)] flex items-center justify-center text-[var(--color-muted)] text-sm">Img</div>
          <div class="p-4">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] group-hover:text-[var(--color-accent)]">Cuidados pós-parto</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-1">Saúde e recuperação da mãe.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-6 text-center">
        <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center min-h-[44px] px-5 py-2.5 rounded-md bg-[var(--color-accent)] text-white text-sm font-medium hover:opacity-90">Ver todos os artigos</a>
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-lg border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-rosa)]/40 p-8 text-center" aria-labelledby="newsletter-title">
      <h2 id="newsletter-title" class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">Newsletter</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-4">Receba dicas e novidades no seu e-mail, sem spam.</p>
      <form class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center max-w-sm mx-auto" action="#" method="post" aria-label="Newsletter">
        <label for="newsletter-email" class="sr-only">E-mail</label>
        <input id="newsletter-email" type="email" name="email" placeholder="seu@email.com" class="flex-1 min-h-[44px] px-4 rounded-md border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-white text-[var(--color-text)]" required />
        <button type="submit" class="min-h-[44px] px-5 py-2.5 rounded-md bg-[var(--color-accent)] text-white text-sm font-medium hover:opacity-90">Inscrever</button>
      </form>
    </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
